        <title>Windows 技能｜一劳永逸的禁用 NT QQ 的更新</title>
        <link>https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 19 Apr 2025 13:27:15 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/QQ.png" alt="Featured image of post Windows 技能｜一劳永逸的禁用 NT QQ 的更新" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;在QQNT的某个版本更新之后，通过修改 Hosts 禁用 QQ 自动更新提示的方法已不可用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;接下来我将介绍最新的禁用 QQ 自动更新提示的方法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开 QQ 自动更新下载的安装包目录，为 &lt;strong&gt;C:\Users&amp;lt;你的用户名&amp;gt;\AppData\Roaming\QQ\packages 右键 full&lt;/strong&gt; 文件夹， 选择属性。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在 &lt;strong&gt;常规&lt;/strong&gt; 选项卡页面中的属性，将 &lt;strong&gt;只读&lt;/strong&gt; 打勾。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/001.png&#34;
	width=&#34;421&#34;
	height=&#34;581&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/001_hu_fcb223e87a2e3ca1.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/001_hu_277a6acbf5caf18d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;full 文件夹的属性页面&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;72&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;173px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择 &lt;strong&gt;安全&lt;/strong&gt; 选项卡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择 &lt;strong&gt;高级&lt;/strong&gt; 。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在 &lt;strong&gt;权限&lt;/strong&gt; 选项卡中选择 &lt;strong&gt;禁用继承&lt;/strong&gt; 并确保下方的选框未勾选。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/002.png&#34;
	width=&#34;895&#34;
	height=&#34;632&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/002_hu_e4e85170d38ee968.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/002_hu_cc1bcfdf5b239e58.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;高级设置，选择禁用继承&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;339px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在弹出的窗口中选择 从此对象中&lt;strong&gt;删除所有已继承的权限&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/003.png&#34;
	width=&#34;352&#34;
	height=&#34;301&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/003_hu_28d05b4de9d00b93.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/003_hu_a0c553f94c3daa61.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;选择第二个&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;116&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;280px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择 &lt;strong&gt;审核&lt;/strong&gt; 选项卡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择 &lt;strong&gt;禁用继承&lt;/strong&gt; 并确保下方复选框&lt;strong&gt;未勾选&lt;/strong&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/004.png&#34;
	width=&#34;895&#34;
	height=&#34;632&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/004_hu_777cabd912d87f12.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/004_hu_200693b1d64f641.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;选择禁用继承&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;339px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;选择 &lt;strong&gt;应用&lt;/strong&gt; ，将会弹出&lt;strong&gt;禁止访问&lt;/strong&gt;的页面。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/005.png&#34;
	width=&#34;892&#34;
	height=&#34;630&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/005_hu_33a44538ad3571ae.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/005_hu_db663ce7c90a6e19.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;禁止访问&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;339px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开 &lt;strong&gt;任务管理器。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;结束名为 &lt;strong&gt;COM Surrogate&lt;/strong&gt; 的进程（仅结束&lt;strong&gt;应用栏目&lt;/strong&gt;的这个进程）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/006.png&#34;
	width=&#34;666&#34;
	height=&#34;619&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/006_hu_5ccd0c20abb26703.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/006_hu_26200c5f26d6cefb.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;任务管理器&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;107&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;258px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;若结束进程后出现下图窗口卡住的问题，请在任务管理器中重新启动文件资源管理器。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/007.png&#34;
	width=&#34;895&#34;
	height=&#34;632&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/007_hu_43a5ee0431d47443.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/007_hu_fb0702291c4109.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;若名为 full的高级安全设置 窗口卡住&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;339px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;以上步骤结束之后，您和其他任何程序将无法访问此文件夹，QQ也将无法下载更新。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/008.png&#34;
	width=&#34;498&#34;
	height=&#34;232&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/008_hu_b466805b96ff6ec8.png 480w, https://www.lanexo.top/p/windows-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8A%B3%E6%B0%B8%E9%80%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8-nt-qq-%E7%9A%84%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0/008_hu_432f9d01ee3e336.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;再次打开 full 文件夹显示上图则代表操作成功&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;214&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;515px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;打开 QQ，选择 设置打开 当有新版本时自动帮我下载并安装。&lt;/p&gt;
